sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Admin/User
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as RHODS Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant DSCCtrl as DSC Controller
    participant CompCtrl as Component Controllers
    participant K8sResources as Kubernetes Resources
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy
    participant User as End User

    Note over Admin,K8sResources: Flow 1: Component Deployment via DataScienceCluster

    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create DataScienceCluster CR<br/>Auth: User Credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-opendatahub-io-v1<br/>mTLS (Service CA)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated DSC (defaults applied)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-opendatahub-io-v1<br/>mTLS (Service CA)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Result
    K8sAPI->>DSCCtrl: Watch Event (DSC Created)<br/>Internal API

    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Component CRs<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Note over DSCCtrl,K8sAPI: Dashboard, Workbenches, KServe,<br/>ModelMesh, DSP, Ray, CodeFlare, etc.

    K8sAPI->>CompCtrl: Watch Event (Component CR Created)<br/>Internal API
    CompCtrl->>K8sAPI: Apply Component Manifests<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Note over CompCtrl,K8sAPI: Deployments, Services, ConfigMaps,<br/>Secrets, RBAC, Routes

    K8sAPI->>K8sResources: Create Resources<br/>Internal
    K8sResources-->>CompCtrl: Resource Created
    CompCtrl->>K8sAPI: Update Component CR Status<br/>Auth: Service Account Token

    Note over Admin,User: Flow 2: Monitoring Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>DSCCtrl: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 Plaintext<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    DSCCtrl-->>Prometheus: Metrics (Prometheus format)

    Prometheus->>K8sResources: Scrape Component Metrics<br/>Various ports/protocols<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    K8sResources-->>Prometheus: Component Metrics

    User->>OAuth: Access Prometheus UI<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: OAuth Token
    OAuth->>K8sAPI: Validate OAuth Token<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>OAuth: Token Valid
    OAuth->>Prometheus: Forward Request<br/>HTTPS/9091 TLS (Service CA)
    Prometheus-->>OAuth: Prometheus UI Response
    OAuth-->>User: Proxied Response

    Note over Admin,K8sResources: Flow 3: Platform Initialization

    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create DSCInitialization CR<br/>Auth: User Credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-opendatahub-io-v1<br/>mTLS (Service CA)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Result
    K8sAPI->>DSCCtrl: Watch Event (DSCI Created)<br/>Internal API

    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Service Mesh Resources<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Note over DSCCtrl,K8sAPI: ServiceMeshMember, DataPlane configs

    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Monitoring Stack<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Note over DSCCtrl,K8sAPI: Prometheus, Alertmanager,<br/>ServiceMonitors, Routes

    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Application Namespace<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Note over DSCCtrl,K8sAPI: redhat-ods-applications,<br/>labels, NetworkPolicies, RBAC

    K8sAPI->>K8sResources: Deploy Infrastructure<br/>Internal
    K8sResources-->>DSCCtrl: Infrastructure Ready
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Update DSCI Status<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
